    @@w+5% spell critical chance@@W.

@@GUnique Psionicist mechanics@@W
  * Prime mortal attribute is @@wIntelligence@@W.
  * Establishes a high-consistency spell-crit baseline for caster paths that
    value frequent critical procs over single-hit spikes.

@@GPsionicist reincarnation bonuses@@W
